{
  "stem": "11722.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "We-- I remember we took a-- a-- [SIGHS] a-- mattresses from these rooms, and we piled them into one room.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we sort of created a hole in between the mattresses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "That's where we slept.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And at night, we would open up the shutters, then we would get some snow and melt it for water.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And then one day, our shutter was opened a little bit, and we noticed a couple civilians approaching this cottage.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And-- and they yanked the thing open.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "My friend jumped aside, and I was frozen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "These two civilians [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] had that scared look on their face like they saw a living skeleton.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I was scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And-- and they told us that the Russians have been in for a couple days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we went to the road.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I remember we had to go up an embankment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the Russians were marching towards Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And there was a Russian Jewish soldier who spoke out to us in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And he took us to a-- this German family, a husband and wife, an elder couple.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And he made them promise to feed us and take care of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And he says, if not, he's going to come back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this German couple cooked for us-- slowly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we ate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I swear I could see myself getting heavier, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was important that we eat slowly and the right food, because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I read where these liberate-- these survivors who were liberated by the Americans, they were given these rich food and their systems couldn't take it, and it was like poison.",
      "word_count": 47
    }
  ],
